// ============================================================================
// END OF MOVEMENT I
//
// The shadows have been cast. The fifth (G-D) is established as fundamental.
// The stepwise cell (D-E-F#-G) has appeared, fragmented. The Long-Short
// rhythm has been heard. But nothing has cohered. The listener carries
// forward a sense of significance without meaning — which is exactly right.
//
// Movement II, "Spectra," will take these fragments and subject them to
// distortion: inversion, displacement, false harmonization. The pursuit
// of the hidden theme becomes more urgent, more frustrated. What was fog
// becomes fever dream.
// ============================================================================
